GSD.description:
ASoC: mediatek: mt8173-rt5650-rt5514: fix refcount leak in mt8173_rt5650_rt5514_dev_probe()

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.9.337 by commit 5f6d57871b805b9eaad608bc76d2f2630616f2cf, it was introduced in version v4.8 by commit 0d1d7a664288f9c1b6f79c971d528a354315e9d3. For more details please see the references link.
